      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of May 12 article about reaction to Mayor Rudolph Giuliani's marital separation; 1987 was when Gary Hart encouraged reporters to follow him about</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A front-page article yesterday about reaction to Mayor Rudolph W. Giuliani's marital separation misstated the year that Gary Hart encouraged reporters to follow him around during his presidential campaign. It was 1987, not 1988.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>A front-page article yesterday about reaction to Mayor Rudolph W. Giuliani's marital separation misstated the year that Gary Hart encouraged reporters to follow him around during his presidential campaign. It was 1987, not 1988.</p>
      </block>
